title: Super One Bedroom - Awesome Summit-Hill location - 614 Portland Ave
neighborhood: St Paul- Just off Summit Ave and Dale St
posting_body: ['We have a wonderful lofted one bedroom apartment available.', ' Contact Eric', 'show contact info', 'for videos and in person showing.', ' FREE PARKING!', 'The Clubhouse, built in 1913, is a stunning combination of past and present with 40 beautifully designed apartments.', 'This grand representative of the historic Summit Hill neighborhood of St. Paul originally housed gymnasium, pool, and bowling alley for the Episcopal Church of St Paul, before transitioning into luxury apartment homes.', 'Apartments retain many original features like high ceilings, pristine woodwork, and oversized windows, while also offering modern touches like marble counters, spacious layouts, updated appliances and air conditioning.', 'The location just off Summit and Grand Avenues can’t be beat!', 'You will have a plethora of shopping and restaurant options within steps of your home, while also having easy access to interstates 94 and 35 and the greater metro area.', 'Come make this landmark your home.', 'We currently have two one bedroom styles available over the next two months.', '- Laundry on site', '- Free parking', '- Super maintenance', '- High ceilings', '- Dishwashers', 'Professionally managed by the Hornig Companies']
